    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>This is an update as Luciano's answer does not work for me: on 2021.2.2, in the windows keymap, the default is <code>Ctrl</code>+ <code>Alt</code> + <code>Shift</code> + <code>arrowKey</code>. You can also change it there.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/cWXqc.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/cWXqc.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\" /></a></p>\n"
